<paragraph id="IAS41_1" principles="yes"><paranum>1</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 41"/><data name="paranum" value="1"/></prolog><body><variant base="SL32827683" id="IAS41_1_V2">       <p id="IAS41_P0012">This Standard shall be applied to account for the following when they relate to <xref base="SL143218" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0104">agricultural activity<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0010"/></ph></xref>:                </p>       <ol base="SL32827687" type="lower-alpha" id="IAS41_L0002"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>           <p base="SL32827689" id="IAS41_P0013"><xref base="SL143220" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0108">biological assets<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0021"/></ph></xref>,                          except for bearer plants;                        </p>         </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>           <p base="SL32827695" id="IAS41_P0014"><xref base="SL143219" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0107">agricultural produce<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0011"/></ph></xref>                          at the point of <xref base="SL143223" href="IAS41_5.dita#IAS41_5/IAS41_P0114">harvest<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0163"/></ph></xref>;                          and</p>         </li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value>           <p base="SL32827706" id="IAS41_P0015"><xref base="SL143247" href="IAS41_8.dita#IAS41_8/IAS41_P0151">government grants<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0150"/></ph></xref>                          covered by <xref base="F32827712" href="IAS41_g34-38.dita#IAS41_g34-38/IAS41_g34-38_TI" id="IAS41_X0071">paragraphs 34 and 35</xref>.</p>         </li></ol>     </variant></body></paragraph>